# The following CVEs are accepted risks for this project.
# All affected packages (cross-spawn, glob, minimatch, tar) are transitive
# dependencies of devDependencies (eslint, nodemon) only.
# The Dockerfile uses `npm ci --omit=dev`, which excludes all devDependencies
# and their transitive packages from the production image.
# These packages are NOT present in the running container.

# cross-spawn - devDep transitive (via eslint)
CVE-2024-21538

# glob - devDep transitive (via eslint)
CVE-2025-64756

# minimatch - devDep transitive (via eslint, nodemon)
CVE-2026-26996
CVE-2026-27903
CVE-2026-27904

# tar - devDep transitive (via nodemon)
CVE-2026-23745
CVE-2026-23950
CVE-2026-24842
CVE-2026-26960
CVE-2026-29786
